<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1132163-what-do-people-make-of-his-use-of-the">What do people make of his use of the N-word? I understand it was commonly used in his time period. Is it considered acceptable to read his work? It&#39;s a shame because otherwise I really like his writing style.</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1132163'><a id="like_count_community_question_1132163" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/1132163?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">3 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F36315.The_Best_of_H_P_Lovecraft">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/1132163-what-do-people-make-of-his-use-of-the">4 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/1132163-what-do-people-make-of-his-use-of-the">See all 4 answers</a>
</li>
</ul>
