      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/work/quotes/1813320-the-best-of-h-p-lovecraft">Quotes from The Best of H.P. ...</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
